org.apache.calcite.rel.type

类 RelDataTypeSystemImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rel.type.RelDataTypeSystemImpl
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    RelDataTypeSystem

    public abstract class RelDataTypeSystemImpl
extends Object
implements RelDataTypeSystem
    Default implementation of RelDataTypeSystem, providing parameters from the SQL standard.

    To implement other type systems, create a derived class and override values as needed.

    Parameter values
    Parameter Value
    MAX_NUMERIC_SCALE 19
